			           README
			===========================

### ABOUT

    Sahana is a free and open source disaster management system. 
    Its main focus is to facilitate returning missing people to
    their families, assisting victims of disasters, allowing
    agencies request and provide support to each other, assiging the
    management of emergency evacuation shelters or temporary camps
    and enhancing inter-agency coordination.
    
    Sahana has recently branched out to support all phases of 
    comprehensive emergency management. Countries, local non-profits
    and international NGOs are utilising Sahana to support risk 
    reduction, readiness, response and recovery operations.


### VERSION

    Trunk

    ## Please note ##
    
    This version has not been comprehensively tested and its code 
    undergoing frequent review. This version is considered unstable
    and you may experience frequent bugs.


