### SUPPORT

    Non-commerical support is provided by a community of global
    volunteers. Please pose your question at any number of the 
    locations below after consulting 
    <http://catb.org/esr/faqs/smart-questions.html>:
   

    1)  Email <sahana-user@lists.sourceforge.net>
        
    2)  Ask your question via our forum-like site at 
        <https://answers.launchpad.net/sahana>
    
    3)  Join us on IRC:
        Network:  Freenode
        Channel:  #sahana 
    
### How to assist with development:

    ## Getting in touch
    
    We welcome support with Sahana's continued development.
    Our main way of keeping in touch is of mailing list:
    
     <https://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/sahana-maindev>

        #sahana on irc.freenode.net

    For those who want more general discussion on Humanitarian ICT,

     <http://groups.yahoo.com/group/humanitarian-ict/>

    ## Learning more about the system
    
    To learn more about how Sahana operates, feel free to visit
    our wiki. Each module, our coding standards and other relevant
    information is documented there: 
    
      <http://www.sahana.lk/wiki/>


Enjoy!!!

  - Sahana Community


